title: Minecraft server is live!
subtitle: Details about the new minecraft server
body:
Minecraft server

The link to the server is mc.twt.gg on Minecraft version 1.17.1 !

If you would like to support the server and buy roles you can do so from https://store.twt.gg/ where right now we are having a 25% launch event sale

Here are the most popular nations on the server

  • Jetbrains
  • VSCountry

title: Tim deleted a video!
subtitle: Tim deleted a video after uploading it! Caught on 4K
body:
Tim deleted a video named Blockchain For Beginners #1 - Smart Contracts With Ethereum & Solidity!

in 10 minutes of uploading - the VIDEO WAS MISSING!!!

The people in general were very fast in finding out that the video went missing. The mystery remains unsolved as we try to find out why Tim deleted the video after uploading it.

UPDATE: Tue, Dec 28:

The video is now back up live! but the reason remains a mystery
